; the internal split-horizon zone for fairlane.tetra.cool. mirrors the mesa zone: @nsIp@ = this
; resolver's IP, @edgeVip@ = the edge ingress VIP (both substituted by nix replaceVars). the
; wildcard answers every *.fairlane.tetra.cool from the edge VIP. serial is static (1) because
; this zone is generated, never hand-edited or transferred.
$TTL 300
$ORIGIN fairlane.tetra.cool.
@   IN SOA ns.fairlane.tetra.cool. hostmaster.fairlane.tetra.cool. (
        1          ; serial
        3600       ; refresh
        900        ; retry
        604800     ; expire
        300 )      ; negative cache ttl
    IN NS  ns.fairlane.tetra.cool.
ns  IN A   @nsIp@
@   IN A   @edgeVip@
*   IN A   @edgeVip@
